Harley Bird https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harley_Bird 0 Harley Bird (born Harley Riley, 13 December 2001) is an English actress and voice-over artist. She is currently known as the third and current voice of Peppa Pig. Harley_Bird ( born Harley_Riley , 13_December_2001 ) is an_English_actress and voice-over_artist .
